<div style="padding: 20px;">
  <p><strong>Questions</strong> are used to verify someone's <strong>progress</strong> through a section. A question can be something the user must do or a picture they must identify, or simply a multiple choice question.</p>
  <p>You have not created any questions for this <%= name_for_paths %> yet. You can get started by:</p>
  <ul>
    <li style="padding:5px;">Creating a <%= link_to "new question manually", new_task_path(:section_id => @section) %>.</li>
    <% if @enable_auto_generate %>
    <li style="padding:5px;">Let Moonlite automatically generate questions from <%= link_to "your section content", questions_section_path(@section) %>.</li>
    <li style="padding:5px;">Let Moonlite automatically generate questions from <%= link_to "text outside of your section content", edit_section_path(@section, :m => "hidden_content") %>.</li>
    <% end %>
  </ul>
</div>